1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 37=

3
00:00:16,559 --> 00:00:17,280
Shuang.

4
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:23,280
Grandfather!

5
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:23,960
Shuang.

6
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:26,039
Shuang.

7
00:00:27,679 --> 00:00:28,839
Shuang, I've failed you.

8
00:00:31,519 --> 00:00:32,920
Wuxia was right.

9
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:35,840
I was far too stubborn.

10
00:00:38,679 --> 00:00:40,600
Grandfather, why did you do it?

11
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:42,200
There are things...

12
00:00:43,390 --> 00:00:44,359
you wouldn't understand.

13
00:00:45,039 --> 00:00:46,359
I want to know.

14
00:00:51,119 --> 00:00:52,119
Everything I did

15
00:00:53,359 --> 00:00:54,759
was for the Gate Bureau.

16
00:00:56,719 --> 00:00:58,000
I did it for the Luo family.

17
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:01,679
Our family has served
the Court for generations.

18
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:04,599
Yet they treat us like common thugs.

19
00:01:05,359 --> 00:01:07,239
They smile when they need us,

20
00:01:07,879 --> 00:01:09,280
but the moment we're useless,

21
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:11,840
they don't even look us in the eye.

22
00:01:11,879 --> 00:01:12,599
Look at the lords

23
00:01:13,239 --> 00:01:15,000
in the Ministry of Justice.

24
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,799
Do you think they care
about a constable?

25
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,439
I am the Commissioner,

26
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,200
yet to them,

27
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:23,840
I am nothing more than a street peddler.

28
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,719
I couldn't accept it.

29
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:29,599
Grandfather.

30
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:35,120
So you wanted
to raise the Gate Bureau's status?

31
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,525
I wanted those elitists

32
00:01:36,525 --> 00:01:38,519
in the Imperial Court to know

33
00:01:39,587 --> 00:01:40,826
that without my Gate Bureau,

34
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,719
the Martial World would fall.

35
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,480
We are just as vital

36
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:47,000
as the Embroidered Guard
or the Eastern Bureau!

37
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:49,000
Then why...

38
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,760
Why did you kill Mr. Mao
and Chu Xiangshan?

39
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:56,599
Chu Xiangshan was an Embroidered
Guard sent by the Emperor

40
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,920
to bury me with charges.

41
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,079
I couldn't let him live.

42
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:00,599
What about Mr. Mao?

43
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:02,680
Why did you have to kill him, too?

44
00:02:03,719 --> 00:02:05,599
He knew things he shouldn't have.

45
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:08,080
As for Jixian's death,

46
00:02:08,512 --> 00:02:09,350
(Sacrificing life for the cause)

47
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,680
I have no excuses.

48
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,199
But Shuang, it was all for the family.

49
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,879
Wuxia is gone.

50
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:18,080
I am a wanted criminal now.

51
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,479
Shuang,

52
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,879
the future of the Luos depends on you.

53
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,719
That is why I came back today.

54
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,360
I need you

55
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,639
to kill me with your own hands.

56
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:38,159
Grandfather, what are you saying?

57
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,960
I am a traitor.

58
00:02:41,159 --> 00:02:41,960
Do you want to spend

59
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,800
your life as the daughter of a criminal?

60
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,639
Only by killing me

61
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,599
can our family survive.

62
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:52,240
It's the only hope we have left.

63
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:55,800
No...

64
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,439
Grandfather, you mustn't.

65
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:59,520
Would you rather
be a traitor's daughter,

66
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:01,000
exiled to the ends of the earth?

67
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,240
Or spend the rest of your life

68
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,879
being trampled by every constable?

69
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,240
Draw your blade.

70
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,780
I refuse to die
at the hands of anyone else.

71
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:17,520
I won't.

72
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:18,719
Grandfather, I can't do it!

73
00:03:18,719 --> 00:03:19,360
Stop saying that!

74
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,159
I won't!

75
00:03:20,159 --> 00:03:22,080
Are you a child
of the Luo family or not?

76
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,879
Grandfather, please!

77
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:24,719
Shuang!

78
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:26,159
Draw your sword!

79
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:28,319
Grandfather, please don't.

80
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:30,159
I'm scared!

81
00:03:36,350 --> 00:03:39,150
(Noble Integrity)

82
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,159
Are you sure it's Luo Shixun?

83
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,639
The men heard his voice, sir.

84
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:45,159
Luo Shixun!

85
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,319
Since you've returned,

86
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,439
(Noble Integrity)
surrender yourself!

87
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:00,719
Shuang...

88
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:05,719
Grandfather!

89
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:06,840
Grandfather!

90
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:07,919
Grandfather!

91
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:09,280
Grandfather, what happened?

92
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:09,919
Grandfather!

93
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:11,120
Grandfather!

94
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,000
Shuang, don't cry.

95
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,079
Don't cry, Shuang.

96
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,519
Our family...

97
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:27,360
The Luo family is in your hands now.

98
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,920
No! Grandfather!

99
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,439
No!

100
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,600
Grandfather!

101
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,040
Grandfather!

102
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:51,759
Grandfather, please wake up!

103
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:54,240
Grandfather!

104
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:00,519
Grandfather!

105
00:05:03,475 --> 00:05:05,425
(Awe-inspiring Righteousness)

106
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,120
Wushuang?

107
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,360
What have you...

108
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,079
Gao Shun, get in there and check.

109
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:34,560
Yes.

110
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,199
Yu!

111
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:47,800
Luo Shixun is dead.

112
00:05:58,439 --> 00:05:59,199
Commander Mao.

113
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:02,439
I have

114
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:05,759
executed the fugitive, Luo Shixun.

115
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,040
Mission completed.

116
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,199
Hear the order!

117
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:25,639
Luo Wushuang,
former constable of the Field Corps,

118
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:27,639
(Gate Bureau, Ministry of Justice)
chose justice over blood.

119
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:29,759
By eliminating Luo Shixun,
she has shown loyalty

120
00:06:29,759 --> 00:06:30,759
and courage.

121
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:32,879
Luo Wushuang is hereby reinstated

122
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:35,040
to her post
as constable of the Field Corps.

123
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,040
End of decree.

124
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,160
My thanks, Commissioner.

125
00:07:00,187 --> 00:07:01,725
(Yunchang Flower Shop)

126
00:07:04,675 --> 00:07:06,040
(Yunchang Flower Shop)

127
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,670
- Success and prosperity to you!
- Prosperity to all!

128
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,920
Congratulations, boss!

129
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:14,240
Friends and neighbors!

130
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,639
Today is the grand reopening
of Yunchang Flower Shop!

131
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:17,639
The owner has declared

132
00:07:17,639 --> 00:07:19,759
a "buy one, get one free" special today!

133
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,240
Come forward and see the owner

134
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,439
to claim your free flowers!

135
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:25,480
- Wonderful!
- Let's go!

136
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,480
How generous!

137
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,639
Hurry, let's go get some!

138
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:28,000
Right!

139
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,480
Here you go.

140
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:30,390
- Thank you.
- Much appreciated!

141
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,879
Come on, let's take a look.

142
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:33,480
One for you.

143
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,319
Thank you, Miss!

144
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,790
- Look at these!
- So beautiful.

145
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,759
This is lovely.

146
00:07:36,820 --> 00:07:37,759
They smell incredible.

147
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:38,319
Thank you.

148
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:39,519
- Many thanks!
- Thank you, Miss.

149
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:40,360
They're gorgeous!

150
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:40,879
Thanks so much.

151
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,610
- Mother, I want one too!
- Best of luck with the shop!

152
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:43,879
Alright, let's go get you one.

153
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,720
Congratulations on your reopening.

154
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:53,600
Everything feels like a long,
strange dream.

155
00:07:54,319 --> 00:07:56,079
If only Wuxia
were still here to see this.

156
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:04,000
We all thought he was
just a spoilt brat.

157
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,800
But he was playing
the fool to hide his brilliance.

158
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:09,800
Everything he did

159
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,160
was to protect the Luo family from ruin.

160
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,639
But Luo Shixun could never see that.

161
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,439
Now that Luo Shixun is gone

162
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:20,360
and Wushuang is back at her post,

163
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:22,720
the family is
finally back on the right path.

164
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:25,519
I think Wuxia

165
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:27,759
can finally rest in peace.

166
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,080
Once this final matter is settled,

167
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,519
I'll truly be at peace.

168
00:08:35,879 --> 00:08:37,080
Did he come looking for you?

169
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,320
Exactly as you predicted.

170
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,519
He was here.

171
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:43,600
It looks like
the final piece of the puzzle

172
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:45,039
is about to fall into place.

173
00:09:23,612 --> 00:09:31,325
(Token)

174
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,879
With the Sacred Token in my hand,

175
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:42,200
no one in the Martial World
can challenge me.

176
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,519
Well, well, the Director of Personnel.

177
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:51,879
You were actually

178
00:09:52,639 --> 00:09:54,639
the real mastermind all along.

179
00:10:04,225 --> 00:10:10,425
(Great Virtue)

180
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,320
So it was you.

181
00:10:23,759 --> 00:10:25,120
How did you figure it out?

182
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,759
I've suspected it for a while.

183
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,759
Luo Shixun was arrogant,

184
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,879
but he was nothing more than a thug.

185
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,960
He didn't have the brains
for a scheme like this.

186
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,639
I knew someone had to
be pulling the strings.

187
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:38,000
That's why I feigned capture

188
00:10:38,159 --> 00:10:39,200
to see who was

189
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:41,759
desperate enough
to interrogate me in my cell.

190
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:44,519
You, a Director of Personnel,

191
00:10:44,639 --> 00:10:46,559
came to save me just

192
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,720
to get a statement.

193
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,279
It was too convenient.

194
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:50,440
When I told you

195
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,399
the Sacred Token
was inside the Gate Bureau,

196
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,279
you didn't look surprised at all.

197
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:56,000
That proved you already knew.

198
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,720
A man obsessed with that token

199
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:58,679
would never pass up

200
00:10:58,679 --> 00:11:00,120
such a golden opportunity.

201
00:11:00,759 --> 00:11:03,639
You used the chaos to steal the real one.

202
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:04,679
And naturally,

203
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,759
the first to come asking for it afterward

204
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,519
had to be the mastermind.

205
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:11,000
I've been investigating you.

206
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,879
After Luo Shixun fell,

207
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,320
you went to the Ghost Market

208
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,759
to have gold and silver replicas made.

209
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:19,080
The token you gave the Ministry

210
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:19,879
is a fake.

211
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:20,879
The real one

212
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,279
is still in your bag.

213
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,080
Mao Buyu.

214
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,639
I accounted for every variable,

215
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:33,320
but I never expected you
to be an Embroidered Guard.

216
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,759
You're also

217
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:38,080
responsible for my father's death.

218
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:44,759
So you found out about that too.

219
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:47,840
The day my father went
to the Personnel Corps to see you,

220
00:11:48,279 --> 00:11:48,960
he caught you

221
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,000
red-handed

222
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,840
altering the records.

223
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,320
He started to suspect you.

224
00:11:59,812 --> 00:12:03,100
(Vice Minister Li Wen, Yangling native.
Modest and upright, noble character.)

225
00:12:03,562 --> 00:12:07,012
(Vice Minister Li Wen, Yangling native.
Rampant bribery and corruption.)

226
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:20,559
(From that moment on,)

227
00:12:20,850 --> 00:12:22,519
he grew suspicious of you.

228
00:12:22,740 --> 00:12:24,200
He began investigating you in secret.

229
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,610
He discovered that for years,

230
00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:27,840
you've exploited your position

231
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,120
to gather dirt

232
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:32,440
on every official in the Gate Bureau

233
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:34,039
and the Ministry of Justice.

234
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,639
You used that leverage

235
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,639
to turn them all into your puppets.

236
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,879
From the Gate Bureau to the Ministry,

237
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:42,320
you were the one who decided who rose

238
00:12:42,679 --> 00:12:44,120
and who fell.

239
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,080
Because you

240
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:47,440
are the true mastermind behind it all.

241
00:12:50,679 --> 00:12:52,759
So, you've finally figured it out.

242
00:12:53,639 --> 00:12:55,000
Because of a single slip-up,

243
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:57,080
Mr. Mao found a crack in your story.

244
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,320
He investigated you in secret.

245
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:00,360
You were terrified
the truth would come out,

246
00:13:00,519 --> 00:13:01,759
so you decided to silence him.

247
00:13:01,879 --> 00:13:02,759
And my father

248
00:13:02,759 --> 00:13:05,080
was hunting
for the Sacred Token at the time.

249
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:08,240
So you goaded Luo Shixun
into doing your dirty work.

250
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,790
You pitted Mao Buyu
and me against each other,

251
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:13,080
while you played both sides
for your own gain.

252
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:03,600
You old scoundrel.

253
00:14:03,919 --> 00:14:05,360
This is pure madness.

254
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,879
This is all pure speculation.

255
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,440
You have no proof.

256
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:12,390
This is the secret scroll
I pulled from the Personnel Corps.

257
00:14:13,075 --> 00:14:13,887
(Personnel Corps)

258
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:18,080
The real Sacred Token
is right there on you.

259
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,360
Stop denying it.

260
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:22,519
Chu Yunchang...

261
00:14:23,639 --> 00:14:25,120
you really are impressive.

262
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:26,279
I also know

263
00:14:26,639 --> 00:14:28,080
you're tied to the bloodbath

264
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,440
from years ago.

265
00:14:30,519 --> 00:14:31,200
Back then?

266
00:14:33,759 --> 00:14:36,440
My grandfather and Luo Shixun

267
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,519
became sworn brothers
over the Gold-Threaded Armor case.

268
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,200
After their pact,

269
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:43,320
Luo Shixun was prepared
to hand the armor over.

270
00:14:43,639 --> 00:14:45,080
It was meant to be an honorable act.

271
00:14:45,679 --> 00:14:48,559
But you found a vulnerability to exploit.

272
00:14:53,887 --> 00:14:57,162
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

273
00:14:57,200 --> 00:15:00,075
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

274
00:15:00,575 --> 00:15:06,293
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

275
00:15:07,475 --> 00:15:10,795
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

276
00:15:10,925 --> 00:15:13,845
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

277
00:15:15,013 --> 00:15:20,253
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

278
00:15:21,475 --> 00:15:23,868
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

279
